The correct terminology is PC-Clone or PClone.  A "clone" is nondenominational;
it could be a PClone, an Amiga Clone, a keyword to the "Copy" command, or a
prize bull for that matter.

>If he meant Amiga clones he would have said "Amiga clones" because a clone 
